Introduction to website

Our Story

History of StudBud

Our original intention for building this website is based on providing love and compassion for students need extra help and support. We collected information and data in relation to our targeted users to gain insights in order to further ideate our website. From the gathered user feedbacks we analysed painpoints from each persona and thoughtfully adjusted features according to user needs. The prototypes from the beginning were roughly sketched and lack of detail. The final presentation of our website is a version built with efforts and considerations, the improvements are significant with more resonable arrangements in accordance to a standard web design layout.

Reflections

The css designs are carefully planned to suit the chosen theme, with images respond to the general aesthetics. I referenced from a series of existing designs, lectures and slack helps to address any technical difficulties I faced furing the implementation and really worked to push the website to the best of my abilitiy. However, there are higher level concepts I was not able to attain further such as retrieving relevant data from a specific library. Overall, the development is the best version for now. I would definitely like to upgrade it further to a full functional website.
